        "TileImage": "$($repository 0e533277-1b15-473a-aa1a-3a6a29918fa6).Image",
        "Description": "So, what do you see on this Picture?\r\rI see a machine of destruction. Calculated and ruthless.\r\rInteresting. And what about this picture?\r\rIt is..almost unspeakable...dreadful creatures spewing out of the jaws of evil.\rLike some kind of host, that just keeps spawning new terrors.\rArgh...it hurts! Please put this out of my sight!\r\rI am sorry 74, I don&apos;t think you are ready. To complete this assignment to have to face your fea...\r\rNO! You are wrong. Pictures mean nothing. I am ready.\r\rBy Celllie",
